import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Helmet } from 'react-helmet';
import GeneralBanner from '../Common/BannerParts/GeneralBanner';

class BasementRenovationsInOakville extends Component {
  static propTypes = {
  };

  state = {
  };

  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Helmet>
          <title>AGM Basements | Basement Renovations in Oakville</title>
        </Helmet>
        <GeneralBanner title="Basement Renovations in Oakville" />
        <div className="container">
          <p>AGM Basements provides first-class quality basement renovation, finishing and building services in Oakville. As basement contractors, we offer competitive pricing without compromising the quality of our work. With over 250 basement projects completed to the satisfaction of clients, you won’t find more experienced or professional basement service providers.</p>

          <h3>Every kind of project</h3>

          <p>When you’re looking for the best basement renovation companies for your basement finishing or basement remodeling, AGM is the only choice. We work in both residential and commercial spaces and are Oakville’s leading basement builders and contractors for basements of any size. We also work on both new builds and older properties – so whatever your needs, call us today and book a free consultation.</p>

          <h3>Care at every step</h3>

          <p>Every basement project is different and at AGM we tailor our services to meet your particular situation. Our well-trained and attentive team will work closely with you at every step of the way – from your free consultation, through design, to assembling the best builders, electricians and cleaners in Oakville to finish your basement.</p>

          <h3>Our guarantee</h3>

          <p>Because we care about delivering quality workmanship at the best possible price, you won’t pay for your basement until it's complete. Our pricing is always transparent – the quote you get is the price you pay. We guarantee the work will be conducted professionally and on schedule and, should the project overrun, we’ll compensate you for the inconvenience. We’ll also use high-quality materials, ensuring we remain the most trusted basement renovation services in Oakville.</p>

          <h3>Our basement finishing services</h3>

          <p>With AGM all estimates are free and your renovation project is managed by skilled technicians at every stage. Our drywall installers are the best in Oakville and we guarantee you’ll be happy with our drywall taping and painting, which encompasses everything from priming to the painting of cove and crown mouldings. High-grade laminate flooring is also included as standard in our basement renovation packages, and all our tiling is completed by installers we employ rather than third parties. Likewise, AGM plumbers are fully licensed and highly competent, and our electricians are also highly experienced.</p>

          <h3>What our clients tell us</h3>

          <p>As the testimonials on this site indicate, our clients often praise our customer service, the reliability of our tradesmen, and our excellent pricing. We’re easy to work with and can often finish a project quicker and to a higher standard than other contractors. With AGM managing your basement work, you can rest assured there will be no shoddy workmanship and no corners cut. We deliver on time, on budget, and in the professional manner you deserve.</p>

          <h3>Call us today</h3>

          <p>Get in touch for a free no-obligation consultation on your project. We’ll talk through your options and, should you request a quote, we’ll be happy to provide one - also at no cost. We won’t make promises we can’t deliver but we do guarantee you’ll get a very competitive price for the work that you need.</p>
        </div>
      </>
    );
  }
}

export default BasementRenovationsInOakville;
